    "body" : "<p>There is the solution with Kotlin :</p>\n\n<pre><code>given(myObject.myCall()).willAnswer {\n    throw IOException(\"Ooops\")\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Where given comes from </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>import org.mockito.BDDMockito.given</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
